video.title: Kim's Convenience
video.synopsis: While running a convenience store in Toronto, members of a Korean-Canadian family deal with customers, each other and the evolving world around them.

episodes.synopsis: Appa's plan to offer customers a "gay discount" hits a few snags. Meanwhile, Umma pressures Janet to get a boyfriend.
episodes.title: Gay Discount

episodes.synopsis: Appa gives Janet unsolicited tips on taking better photos, much to her annoyance. Jung tries for a promotion at the car rental agency.
episodes.title: Janet's Photos

episodes.synopsis: Appa is skeptical when Gerald asks to take his photo for an assignment. Jung clashes with Kimchee at work.
episodes.title: Ddong Chim

episodes.synopsis: With his air conditioning on the fritz, Appa hires a repairperson -- who's very chatty. Jung scores a bonus for a job well done. Janet's cousin visits.
episodes.title: Frank & Nayoung

episodes.synopsis: Eager to see Mr. Chin in a relationship, Appa offers to be his wingman. Janet asks Jung for help with a leaking pipe at the store.
episodes.title: Wingman

episodes.synopsis: Curious how Kimchee suddenly has money to spare, Jung does some sleuthing. Appa gets into a dispute with Janet's professor over parenting styles.
episodes.title: Rude Kid

episodes.synopsis: Jung runs into an old flame at work. Meanwhile, Appa is less than impressed with the methods used by Janet's hapkido teacher.
episodes.title: Hapkido

episodes.synopsis: A new female pastor strikes a chord with Appa. Jung's worlds collide when his friend starts dating his sister.
episodes.title: Service

episodes.synopsis: Are "Best Before" dates on canned food meaningless? Appa is about to find out. Meanwhile, Jung surprises his mom by helping out at church.
episodes.title: Best Before

episodes.synopsis: When Janet lands a new job that actually pays, Gerald steps in to fill her shoes at the convenience store.
episodes.title: Janet's New Job

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious gentleman pays Umma a surprise visit. Kimchee asks Appa for help with his broken toilet.
episodes.title: Handyman

episodes.synopsis: Appa receives some distressing news, which he struggles to share. Jung accompanies Shannon to a work event.
episodes.title: Appa's Lump

episodes.synopsis: Umma tries to recruit Jung -- not Janet -- to sing at the church festival. Appa takes a shine to his swanky new ride.
episodes.title: Family Singing Contest

episodes.synopsis: Jung worries his time to ask Shannon to go on a date is running out. Janet and Gerald are forced to put their apartment plans on hold.
episodes.title: Janet’s Roommate

episodes.synopsis: With a local business award up for grabs, Appa is feeling a little jumpy. Jung tries to get Shannon into cycling.
episodes.title: Business Award

episodes.synopsis: Umma invites Pastor Nina to move in while her apartment is renovated. Jung crashes Janet and Gerald's trivia night.
episodes.title: House Guest

episodes.synopsis: When Nayoung visits, a white lie leads to romantic chaos. Meanwhile, Umma brings a life-size cardboard cutout of Jung to the store.
episodes.title: Cardboard Jung

episodes.synopsis: Janet urges her dad to step up his romance game during a date night with Umma. Jung stains Kimchee's collector-item sneakers and hunts to replace them.
episodes.title: Date Night

episodes.synopsis: While visiting their future burial plots, Appa and Umma make an unfortunate discovery. A faux fight between Jung and Kimchee is caught on video.
episodes.title: Resting Place

episodes.synopsis: Appa and Umma learn that selling illegal face cream has a downside. Janet adopts an alternate identity to get into a film festival.
episodes.title: Sneak Attack

episodes.synopsis: In hopes of claiming a winning lotto ticket, Janet searches for a legal loophole. Jung has a tough talk with Shannon. Umma covets a fancy coat.
episodes.title: Silent Auction

episodes.synopsis: Kimchee tries to keep his new girlfriend from meeting Jung. Janet speaks her mind in class. Appa scores a new TV.
episodes.title: New TV

episodes.synopsis: Janet struggles to keep her parents from learning about her relationship with Raj. Meanwhile, Jung and Kimchee plan a party.
episodes.title: Janet’s Boyfriend

episodes.synopsis: Kim's Convenience gets a noisy new neighbor. Jung becomes smitten with a new co-worker. Gerald's new girlfriend rubs Janet the wrong way.
episodes.title: Good Neighbours

episodes.synopsis: Appa inherits his daughter's old smartphone. Umma finds a stray dog in the store. Janet and Kimchee bond over dim sum.
episodes.title: Appa’s First Text

episodes.synopsis: At a party to celebrate getting his GED, Jung can't ignore his feelings for Shannon. Meanwhile, Janet grows tired of standing in her brother's shadow.
episodes.title: Handy Graduation

episodes.synopsis: Appa's got a plan to get a new appliance for less, Jung looks to mend old fences and Janet searches for a way to differentiate herself online.
episodes.title: New Appa-liance

episodes.synopsis: Appa worries Umma will be jealous of a flirty online review. Jung returns to his old stomping grounds. Gerald's girlfriend ruffles Janet's feathers.
episodes.title: Cutie Pie

episodes.synopsis: Appa and Umma take their bickering to a new level. Janet crosses paths with a photography idol. Shannon's boyfriend asks Jung for a favor.
episodes.title: Open Kimunication

episodes.synopsis: Appa has a solution for spotty Wi-Fi -- use the neighbor's. Jung has eyes for Shannon's friend. Umma and Pastor Nina ask Janet to do a church reading.
episodes.title: Thy Neighbour's Wifi

episodes.synopsis: Gerald photographs Appa -- and his spoon -- for an exhibit. Janet's apology for a restaurant faux pas doesn't go well. Umma receives an alarming call.
episodes.title: Army Spoon

episodes.synopsis: An old pingpong table rekindles a rivalry between Appa and Jung. Umma sets out to bond with Janet but finds Chelsea to be more receptive.
episodes.title: The Kim Cup

episodes.synopsis: Appa's quest to retrieve his drill from Janet leads to an amorous encounter with Umma. Jung gives Kimchee unsolicited advice -- and plenty of it.
episodes.title: Appanoon Delight

episodes.synopsis: Following Appa's spelling error, Umma becomes the store signmaker. Kimchee's mom visits. Janet lands an internship -- for Gerald.
episodes.title: To Him It May Concern

episodes.synopsis: Appa and Umma search for an excuse to avoid vacationing with the Lees. Janet scores a lucrative -- but awkward -- photography gig.
episodes.title: Blabber Talker

episodes.synopsis: Kimchee gets conflicting dating advice from Jung and Shannon. Janet's outraged when she learns that Umma's sold off her childhood keepsakes.
episodes.title: Elephant in the Room

episodes.synopsis: Appa gives Umma feedback on an annoying habit -- and promptly regrets it. Janet bumps into an old flame. Jung considers giving reality TV a shot.
episodes.title: Appanticitis

episodes.synopsis: A small fender bender leads to a big argument between Appa and Umma. Jung second-guesses a birthday greeting. Janet goes from mocker to mocked.
episodes.title: Hit 'n' Fun

episodes.synopsis: Umma tries to find her missing wedding ring before Appa does. Jung crashes Janet's yoga class.
episodes.title: Lord of the Ring

episodes.synopsis: As Janet and Raj muddle through the fallout of his broken engagement, Mr. Kim tries to return his wife's dress and Shannon does an awkward impression.
episodes.title: The Trollop

episodes.synopsis: After a water pipe bursts at their apartment building, Jung stays with Janet while Kimchee crashes with the Kims.
episodes.title: Couch Surfing

episodes.synopsis: When Umma is mistaken for a server at Janet's art show, Janet sets out to address unconscious bias. Also, Shannon and Alejandro call it quits.
episodes.title: The Help

episodes.synopsis: Janet volunteers to host an anniversary dinner for Umma and Appa. Shannon and Jung try to keep their relationship a secret.
episodes.title: Happy Ummaversary

episodes.synopsis: Umma gets some gossip about Pastor Nina. Janet volunteers to help out an ex. Jung is surprised to learn it's his and Shannon's five-week-iversary.
episodes.title: Thinkin’ ‘bout Inkin’

episodes.synopsis: Appa crashes Jung and Kimchee's soccer match. Shannon goes full steam ahead on planning a birthday party for Stacie. Janet tries to cook like Umma.
episodes.title: Soccer Dad

episodes.synopsis: Janet reveals she lied to Appa in high school. Meanwhile, Umma is asked to boot Mrs. Mehta from the book club and Shannon annoys Jung at work.
episodes.title: Beacon of Truth

episodes.synopsis: Shannon wants to be pals with Janet, who isn't really into the idea. Umma asks Jung to pick up Appa from the dentist.
episodes.title: Chammo!

episodes.synopsis: Umma stumbles across some of Janet's unflattering childhood drawings. Appa takes his good luck and pays it forward. Shannon shows off her moves.
episodes.title: Which Witch is Which

episodes.synopsis: Appa's snoring has Umma at her wit's end and ready to make some changes. Eager to try modeling, Jung asks Janet to take some headshots.
episodes.title: In the Bedroom

episodes.synopsis: An injured bird tests Jung's patience and compassion. Appa gives a seminar at church. Janet learns her plan to visit Korea is a popular one.
episodes.title: Birds of a Feather

episodes.synopsis: Mr. Kim's complaint about the police leads to action. Shannon and Kimchee attend a harsh company meeting.
episodes.title: Knife Strife

episodes.synopsis: With her personal life in chaos, Janet mulls a big opportunity. Meanwhile, Jung considers a move of his own. Also, Appa and Umma hit the beach.
episodes.title: Bon Voyage

episodes.synopsis: Appa reaps the benefits of Umma's accessible parking pass. Janet embraces a new ambition. Shannon and Jung spice up their long-distance romance.
episodes.title: Parking Pass

episodes.synopsis: A local celebrity takes over Umma's announcement duties at church. Appa takes issue with Janet's journaling. Shannon allows shorts in the office.
episodes.title: Channouncements

episodes.synopsis: Appa unknowingly ruins Gerald's baby blanket. Jung invites Kimchee for a weekend in California. Janet tries to convince Umma to join a support group.
episodes.title: Appa & Linus

episodes.synopsis: Appa and Umma sneak into a fancy neighborhood to play tennis. Shannon gives Omar dubious advice. Janet befriends a coworker.
episodes.title: Tennis Anyone?

episodes.synopsis: Cousin Nayoung arrives with an unconventional pet. Jung and Shannon have a stressful lunch with Umma. Kimchee ignores a coworker's feelings.
episodes.title: A Tangled Web

episodes.synopsis: Janet is in the hot seat when Appa finds marijuana in the house. Meanwhile, Shannon is overwhelmed trying to throw a party for her employees.
episodes.title: Cookie Monster

episodes.synopsis: Kimchee worries about how his relationship with Appa may impact Jung. Janet finds an envelope full of cash. Shannon's chatting drives Jung bonkers.
episodes.title: Chance Encounter

episodes.synopsis: A minor accident leaves Appa worried for Umma’s safety. Janet passes off Jung's troubled history as her own. Kimchee gets curious about an old flame.
episodes.title: Slippery Slope

episodes.synopsis: Appa's reputation as an impartial umpire faces a stiff test. Jung and Kimchee disagree about discipline. Janet worries a sweater may be haunted.
episodes.title: Field of Schemes

episodes.synopsis: Kimchee's plan to impress the higher-ups backfires. Shannon inadvertently insults Umma's cooking. Appa and Janet enter a prank war.
episodes.title: Who's Pranking Who?

episodes.synopsis: Umma tries to set up Janet with their new mason. Shannon encourages Jung to give Appa a gift. Kimchee and Shannon work on employee evaluations.
episodes.title: Matchy Matchy

episodes.synopsis: Janet and Appa take a first aid course. Umma worries her prayers cause more harm than good. Shannon and Jung discuss their relationship.
episodes.title: Hugs & Prayers

episodes.synopsis: Janet tries to convince Appa and Umma to hear out Jung's business ideas. Shannon and Jung struggle to stay connected during a rough patch.
episodes.title: Family Business
